    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document discusses multi-endpoint topologies used in Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP)-based environments.  In particular, centralized topologies commonly employed in the video conferencing industry are mapped to the RTP terminology.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
